Text: Vart ska jag l채gga PSIKey.dll? Filen som ligger i Crack mappen?
how do I install this program. I cannot open this file
What is the serial so i can use this damn software????

No serial needed, install as test-version. 
After first start close the program and copy the PSIkey.dll from the Crack folder into the Progam folder of Corel Designer 12. The nag-screen goes away then.
